{"title":"「FJSC2018TGD1T2」 余数求和","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":["提高","数论"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5032#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=5032","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5032/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5032/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/5032"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"给出正整数 $n$ 和 $k$，计算 $j(n, k)=k \\mod 1 + k \\mod 2 + k \\mod 3 +\\cdots + k \\mod n$ 的值。其中 $k \\mod i$ 表示 $k$ 除以 $i$ 的余数。 \r\n\n\r\n\n例如 $j(5, 3)=3 \\mod 1 + 3 \\mod 2 + 3 \\mod 3 + 3 \\mod 4 + 3 \\mod 5=0+1+0+3+3=7$\r\n\n"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入仅一行，包含两个整数n, k。\r\n\n"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出仅一行，即 $j(n, k)$ 。\r\n\n\r\n\n"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"【输入样例】\r\n````\r\n5 3\r\n````\r\n【输出样例】\r\n````\r\n7\r\n````\r\n"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\le n ,k \\le 10^9$\r\n\n\r\n\n数据有梯度。"}]}